content.html: 100 million eligible voters chose not to vote in 2016. “Both parties are the same.” “My vote doesn’t matter.” 🙄 Here is one result of that foolishness. Hillary Clinton would not have nominated Kavanaugh, Gorsuch, and Barrett. Biden can’t solve this by executive order.
